Subject: UNABLE TO SELECT COMPUTERS IN GREY
Description:
Hi Team,

We start today to update the agent from version 5.8.4.1 to version 6.2.3.1, but when we create an update job some computers in online are in grey, and we are unable to select them, Could you help us to know why?

Solution_Comment__c: Solved by removing the old upgrade jobs
